subject: Hello sir/Madam,
body:
Hello sir/Madam,
Notifications! ! !
Your email is one of our lucky winner(s) in the just concluded email ballot system, please contact the undersigned for every information regarding your winning.
Thus we are sorry for not sending your winning information along, we do not want to send to the wrong recipient.
Once we receive your respond, all information about your winning will be sent to you accordingly.
The Fiducial Office

subject: Re: Hello sir/Madam,
body:
Hello! Thank you for reaching out. I'm interested to learn more about my supposed winnings. Can you please provide me with further details on how to proceed?

Best wishes,
Fred
